Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The final flight of the SR-71 Blackbird
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yg2x6
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 9 Mar 1990
The final flight of the SR-71 Blackbird spy plane, the Russian capture of an American pilot in 1960 and the cuts in the American public spending budgets.